description: PRODUCT OVERVIEWUnfold a world of possibilities with Galaxy Z Fold4. It’s more than just a phone it's a foldable powerhouse that allows you to do more from the palm of your hand.KEY FEATURESFlex Mode - Free up your hands with Flex Mode on Galaxy Z Fold4. It stands on its own so you can take notes during a conference call or follow along with instructional videos in real time.Hands-free video - Don’t stay stuck to your phone. Set up your phone in Flex Mode and check off your to-dos while catching up with friends. Hands-free video chat lets you multitask and move freely while staying in frame.Multi-window view - Take the art of doing to a whole new level with Galaxy Z Fold4 Easily attend a virtual work meeting and capture important notes at the same time, or catch up on your favorite shows as you answer texts.With multiple windows, doing different tasks is easy with Galaxy Z Fold4.S Pen - Transform your Galaxy Z Fold4 into a multi-functional device with S Pen.It gives you that pen-on-paper feeling and makes it easy to take notes while attending virtual meetings, drag and drop content and get more done —no matter where you go.¹App optimization - It’s your apps, your way. App display optimization allows you to customize how you see apps on the edge-to-edge screen of Galaxy Z Fold4Also, use multiple apps to their full potential by dragging and dropping content from one window to the other.Ecosystem (Galaxy Watch) - Unfold the possibilities of your Galaxy Z Fold4 connected to your Watch. Use your Watch to snap hands-free selfies with Flex Mode. Plus, keep track of your day by easily switching between your Galaxy Watch and Galaxy Z Fold4.Ecosystem (Galaxy Buds) - Experience movies and videos big and loud with your Galaxy Z Fold4 and Buds in sync. Need to head out while you’re in the middle of your favorite podcast?Slide Galaxy Z Fold4 into your pocket and keep listening with your Buds.
